# Repository Index for autoload directory
# This file describes the purpose of this directory for AI agents

tag: autoload-singletons
purpose: Godot Autoload scripts - global scriptes that persist across scenes and load first/unload last.
Contains:
1. Environment runtime, an entry for the core environemnt-system structure. Should always run first.
2. Node-based controllers that bridge between the scene tree and Systems, providing scene tree capabilities to RefCounted Systems. Controllers do NOT manage System lifecycle - see docs/developer.md

